Enum Class TokenType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TokenType>
interpreteur.TokenType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TokenType>, Constable
public enum TokenType extends Enum<TokenType>
The TokenType enum represents the different types of tokens that can be identified by the lexer.
